<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />Do not hide your face from me;</para>

<para style="q1">do not turn your servant away in anger!</para>

<para style="q1">You have been my helper;</para>

<para style="q1">do not forsake me or abandon me, God of my salvation!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />Even if my father and my mother forsake me,</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh will take me in.</para>
